text: I was there with my girl friend. We order Octopus, duck, ribs and ham. They gave us 2 long joined tables which was for 6 persons . When I asked to sperate these tables to be more confortable with my girl, they said NO, we can not move 1 feet. \nSo disappointed. I just wanna make 1 feet space in our area, and seat near to her. \nTheir food quality is good, but customer servis and customer management  NO.
All perfect here, nice place & good price!
Their food is good a little pricey but worth it. Has a nice ambience.

My husband and I have been coming to this restaurant since we first started dating and it’s just fantastic. We just got the takeout multi course meal with wine deal from GILT City to use for our 4th anniversary dinner.  There was a slight hiccup when I went to pickup but their professionalism just showed why this has been a favorite restaurant of ours for years. The food we got was fantastic and we couldn’t finish it all. The lobster paella in particular was a standout. Thank you again for making it a wonderful, special meal. We can’t wait to use our reservation once you have indoor dining again!  I wish I had the managers name to thank her personally but thank you for making it a wonderful night!
The food was so delicious! Me and my family enjoyed it. It filled our empty stomachs. We'll visit again this place next time!
